&lt;p&gt;At Samsara, the Deal Desk&#39;s mission is to secure durable and efficient growth for the company through best-in-class, agile and scalable deal governance. The Deal Desk Director for Enterprise will lead Samsara’s Deal Desk function for US/Canada Enterprise segments.&lt;/p&gt;
